subSubSection.paragraph:
Pale grey to dark brown spiders, with uniform colouration of body (
Figure 1C
) or clearly patterned body and banded legs (
Figure 1B
), ventral opisthosoma with distinct dark marking (
Figure 23
B-D) or pale (
Figure 23A
), dorsal opisthosoma with a pattern of small chevrons in posterior half.
